{"tid":2109403,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［港共滅絕港人計劃］政府各部門爆武漢肺炎但其他員工要繼續正常返工","createTime":"2020-07-15T08:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T10:25:11.000Z","uid":322400,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6517d05316a14447d2299b435f45280ffc46d494","tid":2109403,"uid":322400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"煲大佢啦喂<br />\n<br />\n利申左先 我朋友係公墓員 <br />\n佢做緊個棟工貿署20樓有人確診 <br />\n但20樓嘅人要繼續正常返工 成棟野都係 <br />\n然後佢有同事個親戚都係入境署做 <br />\n中左招左個度定唔知成棟野又係唔俾dismiss要繼續返工 <br />\n<br />\n真攬炒啦今次 咁多部門都已經瀨左野<br />\n雖然成日屌話唔俾公墓員wfh<br />\n但大家諗下啲公墓員身邊條友中左招又要繼續返工 <br />\n成日流流長痴滿晒病毒 一陣放工就搭車周圍去 <br />\n全港九新界甚至係你都會俾佢地惹到<br />\n<br />\n個仆街正苦想殺晒全香港嘅人大換血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff48296228c1eabe341ab07fea46802295fb046","tid":2109403,"uid":291230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真攬炒"},{"pid":"36a75b29aa1905d39f77441c1caab44d3e901242","tid":2109403,"uid":206687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"根據7婆同陳姑娘個logic<br />\n公務員特殊體質 冇需要WFH"},{"pid":"416835afb2f689faf4801b9ba87112d9907f60f2","tid":2109403,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"就算返到寫字樓，都係乜都做唔到"},{"pid":"28f5b1ecffa1e3824822b4a24d612bce1aeb7cca","tid":2109403,"uid":174013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"又唔係緊密接觸者，點解要wfh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最正常做法味咪搵人全棟清消毒清潔一次"},{"pid":"3be3f863d7a8cecab5788d57a7162c2fcac05835","tid":2109403,"uid":322400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"36a75b29aa1905d39f77441c1caab44d3e901242","tid":2109403,"uid":206687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score